# 🎨 Simple Paint App in C#

A lightweight paint application built using **C#** and **Windows Forms**. Perfect for basic drawing, doodling, and experimenting with colors. Ideal for learning graphics programming or just having a little fun! 🖌️🧑‍🎨

---

### 🚀 Features

    ✅ Freehand drawing with the mouse
    🎨 Color picker to change brush color
    ✏️ Adjustable pen thickness (optional)
    🗑️ Clear canvas
    💡 Simple and intuitive UI

---

### 🛠️ Built With

    💻 C#
    🪟 Windows Forms (.NET Framework)

---

Simple Paint App in C#/
├── Form1.cs              # Main paint logic
├── Form1.Designer.cs     # UI layout
├── Form1.resx            # Form resources
├── Program.cs            # Entry point
├── App.config            # App configuration
├── Paint Application.sln # Visual Studio solution
├── Paint Application.csproj # Project file
├── Properties/
└── (bin/, obj/, .vs/)    # Build and IDE files

---


✅ Prerequisites

    Visual Studio (2019 or newer)
    .NET Framework (comes with Visual Studio)

▶️ How to Run
1. Clone the repository or download the zip file.
    bash
    Copy
    Edit
    git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/Simple-Paint-App-CSharp.git
    Open the Paint Application.sln file in Visual Studio.

    Press F5 or click Start to run the app.

